Rip notes: downsampled big audio files

Buggy Heat is an off-road racing game featuring 8 off-road vehicles and 6 tracks based on locations around the world. There are several modes of play : Time Attack mode, where you make your own Driving Style, Vs Mode, Championship Mode and  AI Level Mode, where you can test your driving skills.

* Complete car customization : from suspension and braking to paint schemes and decals!
* Replay mode with customizable cameras !
* Revolutionary Autopilot Feature : save your Driving Style to your VMU, then trade VMU's to virtually compete with others!